text: Dettingen is the name of four places in Germany: * Dettingen an der Erms, a municipality in the district of Reutlingen in Baden-Württemberg * Dettingen an der Iller, a municipality in the district of Biberach in Baden-Württemberg * Dettingen unter Teck, a municipality in the district of Esslingen in Baden- Württemberg * Dettingen (Rottenburg), a part of the city of Rottenburg am Neckar in the district of Tübingen in Baden-Württemberg
title: Dettingen
